item.title: [HIVE-22435] Exception when using VectorTopNKeyOperator operator
item.description:
Steps to reproduce:
1. Apply the attached patch

git apply -3 -p0 HIVE-20150.15.patch

2. rebuild project

mvn clean install -DskipTests

3. Run the following test

mvn test -DskipSparkTests -Dtest=TestMiniLlapLocalCliDriver -Dqfile=limit_pushdown3.q -pl itests/qtest -Pitests

Query execution fails with exception

select ctinyint, count(distinct(cdouble)) from alltypesorc group by ctinyint order by ctinyint limit 20

[ERROR]   TestMiniLlapLocalCliDriver.testCliDriver:59 Client execution failed with error code = 2 
running

fname=limit_pushdown3.q

VectorTopNKeyOperator extends TopNKeyOperator and it calls it's super.initializeOp method
https://github.com/apache/hive/blob/5c8392468cb581f53b6cb55d201fc933dca025e3/ql/src/java/org/apache/hadoop/hive/ql/exec/vector/VectorTopNKeyOperator.java#L71

which is focusing on non-vectorized execution.

cc. jcamachorodriguez
